-4169-bd83-312787b6b34b\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/A_RES_64_142-EN.pdf\">2009 Guidelines for the Alternative Care of Children (English)<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/A_RES_64_142-EN.pdf\" class=\"wp-block-file__button\" download aria-describedby=\"wp-block-file--media-20a0e827-5a56-4169-bd83-312787b6b34b\">Download<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/digitallibrary.un.org\/record\/673583#record-files-collapse-header\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Click here for other language options.<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This document provides the first in-depth explanation of how the relevant articles of the CRC should be applied to children in alternative care. <\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":5286,"template":"","tags":[53,20],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.2 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>2009 Guidelines for the Alternative Care of Children - Hope and Homes<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"This document provides the first in-depth explanation of how the relevant articles of the CRC should be applied to children in alternative care.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/publications\/2009-guidelines-for-the-alternative-care-of-children\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"2009 Guidelines for the Alternative Care of Children - Hope and Homes\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"This document provides the first in-depth explanation of how the relevant articles of the CRC should be applied to children in alternative care.\" \/>\n<meta property